Question: One flower arrangement is not in a vase.

Reference Answer: True

Right image URL: http://fyf.tac-cdn.net/images/products/large/BF216-11KM.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the flower arrangement in a vase?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the flower arrangement in a vase?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='not {ANSWER0}')
ANSWER3=EVAL(expr='not {ANSWER1}')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER2} xor {ANSWER3}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER4)
```
